short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Find and extract multimedia resources embedded in files

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Find and extract (non-obfuscated) multimedia resources embedded within binary files. Discover hidden images, audio, video or documents.

Currently supported internal resource types: JPG, BMP, GIF, PNG, MP3, WAV, MIDI, WMA, WMV, HTML
